How I have gained lean muscle mass throughout my journey! 🫶🏼⚡️

Remember that gaining lean muscle is a process and you may not progress at the same rate as someone else. These tips are exactly how I achieved my lean bulk to help you on your journey! 😊

STRENGTH TRAINING 🏋🏽‍♀️
It is ideal to strength train at least 3-5 times while including progressive overload to your workouts every 2-3 weeks! Use a variety of two ranges including both lower (4-6 reps) and higher (8-12 reps) to maximize muscle growth and strength gains.

CARDIO 🏃🏽‍♀️
I know we don’t like cardio but it is necessary! I am a sprint interval girl but feel free to add in a HIlT workout, stairmaster, or even a long walk to get some cardio in! These are all efficient ways to burn calories and maintain muscle mass as it involves short bursts of intense exercise followed by periods of rest.

HIGH PROTEIN INTAKE 🌯🍗
This is super important to your journey as high protein meals aid in muscle growth that you want! Depending on your goals, you always want to have a protein intake that is equal to your number in weight!
